@startuml
title Viaverse Quote / Offer — State Diagram

[*] --> DRAFT
DRAFT --> SENT : send
SENT --> QUESTIONED : requester asks
QUESTIONED --> REVISION_REQUESTED : needs change
REVISION_REQUESTED --> REVISED : worker revises
REVISED --> SENT : resend
SENT --> ACCEPTED : requester accepts
REVISED --> ACCEPTED : requester accepts
SENT --> REJECTED : requester rejects
SENT --> WITHDRAWN : sender withdraws
SENT --> EXPIRED : expiresAt
QUESTIONED --> EXPIRED : expiresAt

ACCEPTED --> [*]
REJECTED --> [*]
WITHDRAWN --> [*]
EXPIRED --> [*]

note bottom
ACCEPTED triggers JobCreated and payment flow in the next part.
end note
@enduml
